This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4014

Vitality makes Vim play nicely with iTerm 2 and tmux.

For example: it restores the FocusGained and FocusLost autocommands when running Vim in iTerm 2, even through tmux!

For more information: https://github.com/sjl/vitality.vim
